data.description: Motivated Sellers offering $10K towards buyers closing costs or can be used to help buy down the rate. Come see this gorgeous ready to move in home. It features a modern look with bronze finishes throughout. The home has an attached 3-car garage included. Enter the foyer and find a customizable flex room, perfect for an office or playroom. The family room flows into the kitchen & dining area. On the second floor, four large bedrooms await, with a cozy loft. Your owner's suite offers a large walk-in closet with tray ceiling and luxurious bathroom. Just 5 miles to VA border.
